data.eml:eml: Long-legged cave spiders (Araneae, Telemidae) from Yunnan-Guizhou Plateau, southwestern China

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Lin, Yucheng, Li, Shuqiang (2010): Long-legged cave spiders (Araneae, Telemidae) from Yunnan-Guizhou Plateau, southwestern China. Zootaxa 2445: 1-34, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.195036
